<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>cozone join</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <script type="module" src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.5.2/dist/ionicons/ionicons.esm.js"></script>
    <script nomodule src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.5.2/dist/ionicons/ionicons.js"></script>

    <style>
        * {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #111;
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            /* display: flex; */
            /* align-items: center; */
            /* justify-content: center; */
            /* overflow: hidden; */
            background-image: url("./Frame\ 4.png");
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .contextBox {
            background: #151515;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 27px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 15px;
            width: fit-content;
            padding: 15px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            width: 45%;
            border: 1px solid #292929;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.192);
            position: relative;
            overflow: visible;
            height: 87%;
        }

        .contextBox input {
            width: 96%;
            background: #1B1B1B;
            height: 36px;
            border: 1px solid #292929;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-indent: 6px;
            margin: 4px 0px;
            outline: none;
            color: white;
        }

        .contextBox h2 {
            color: white !important;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 5px 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .buttonRow {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            width: 96%;
            margin: 14px 0px;
        }

        .classic {
            /* width: 100%; */
            border: 1px solid #292929;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            height: 32px;
            width: 170px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: .25s;
        }

        .classic:hover {
            opacity: 0.6;
            transition: .25s;
        }

        .dismiss {
            background: #1B1B1B;
            color: white;
        }

        .enable {
            background: orange;
            color: black;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .opacific {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            color: orange;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: .25s;
            font-size: 13px;
            padding: 7px 17px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 100px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 166, 0, 0.122);
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .opacific:hover {
            opacity: 0.5;
            transition: .25s;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 4vh 4vw;
        }

        header h2 {
            color: orange;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 45px;
            color: white;
            line-height: 45px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        img {
            width: 850px;
            margin: auto;
            display: block;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .pros-grid {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            margin: 60px 0px;
            padding-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .pro {
            width: 400px;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #292929;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.415);
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 16px;
            background-color: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.285);
        }

        .pro h3 {
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: rgba(249, 252, 255, 0.505);
        }

        .pro p {
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        @media (max-width: 1196px) {
            .pros-grid {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .pro {
                margin: 20px 0px;
            }

            img {
                width: 800px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            img {
                width: 650px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 35px;
            }

            .pro {
                width: 80%;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 650px) {
            img {
                width: 500px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 550px) {
            img {
                width: 350px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size:20px;
                line-height: 20px;
            }
        }
</style>

</head>
<body>
    <!-- <div class="contextBox"> -->
    <!-- </div> -->

    <header>
        <h2>cozone</h2>
        <a class="opacific" href="/create">Create Room</a>
    </header>

    <h1>Beautiful, Elegant & Easy-to-use <br> chat rooms</h1>

    <img src="./chatroom.svg" alt="chatroom-svg">

    <div class="pros-grid">
        <div class="pro">
            <h3>Secure & Encrypted</h3>
            <p>
                Your messages are visible
                to you and other participants only. And they
                will be deleted once the last participant leaves
                the chat
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="pro">
            <h3>Easy To Use</h3>
            <p>
                You can get comfortable or "cozy" here. 
                With elegant and easy-to-use UI, get in the
                ZONE. Learn more about this project
                on GitHub 
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>